### PoVicTranslate API Test Suite
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code to execute these requests
### Ensure API is running on localhost:5000 or localhost:5001

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@baseUrlHttp = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check - Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check - Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check - Full Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Translation - Simple Text
POST {{baseUrl}}/translation/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello, how are you today?"
}

###

### Translation - Long Text
POST {{baseUrl}}/translation/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. This is a longer sentence to test the translation service with more complex input."
}

###

### Translation - Empty Text (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/translation/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": ""
}

###

### Translation - Special Characters
POST {{baseUrl}}/translation/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "What's the weather like? It's raining cats and dogs!"
}

###

### Lyrics - Get All Lyrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/lyrics
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics - Get by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/lyrics/{{lyricId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics - Create New
POST {{baseUrl}}/lyrics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Song",
  "artist": "Test Artist",
  "originalLyrics": "Hello world, how are you?",
  "translatedLyrics": "Good morrow, fair world, how dost thou fare?",
  "audioUrl": ""
}

###

### Lyrics - Update Existing
PUT {{baseUrl}}/lyrics/{{lyricId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{lyricId}}",
  "title": "Updated Test Song",
  "artist": "Updated Artist",
  "originalLyrics": "Hello world, how are you?",
  "translatedLyrics": "Good morrow, fair world, how dost thou fare?",
  "audioUrl": "https://example.com/audio.mp3"
}

###

### Lyrics - Delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/lyrics/{{lyricId}}

###

### Audio Synthesis - Generate Speech
POST {{baseUrl}}/audio/synthesize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Good morrow, fair world, how dost thou fare?"
}

###

### Diagnostic - System Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diagnostic
Accept: application/json

